item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I am Arjun. I live in Delhi, India. I am currently in that awkward phase in life where you have finished two years in college and are trying to pivot yourself around a point to what you think is more feasible as a career option than whatever understanding of a career you had as a fresher/sophomore. I am a student of Engineering. What’s the deal with this website ? It’s minimalist.
